## FSD Flexible Schema Data

data first, schema later.

We need to make unstructured data searchable, indexable and queryable

- use RDBMS schema inheritance

- How to deal with very BIG tables in postgresSQL? table with records > 32TB
- TABLE PARTITION Technique : split big table into 2 based on time before and after and
  - write a stored procedure to determine which table to use for further CRUD
